'''Jon Bon Jovi''' is an American musician who made his debut on the [[1980]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Wikipedia:Christmas|Christmas]] album entitled ''[[Christmas in the Stars]]''. On the album, he was credited as '''John Bongiovi'''.<ref name="Christmas">''[[Christmas in the Stars]]''</ref>

With [[George Lucas]]' permission, Bon Jovi named [[Wikipedia:Big & Rich|Big & Rich's]] 2012 album [[Wikipedia:Hillbilly Jedi|''Hillbilly Jedi'']].<ref name="Billboard">{{WebCite|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-615/475075/big-rich-how-bon-jovi-and-george-lucas-named-their-new-album|text=Big & Rich: How Bon Jovi and George Lucas Named Their New Album|author=Gary Graff|date=2012-09-17|work=[[Wikipedia:Billboard (magazine)|''Billboard'']]|archivedate=20130530185033}}</ref>

